name: Small IceBox
description:
Display your kicks all year round or use as a replacement box.  Low tops can be laid on it's side High tops can be sat upright.

Fits most shoes up to men's 10/11 depending on the shoe. Can hold a bigger size one shoe at a time.

Customize to your liking by adding lights, stickers, and materials to enhance the overall look.

IceBox™ is designed in the USA hand made in China.

Lights and Shoes not included.
